15. I'm On Your Side - Kathy Mattea[/b]
 
 By A Customer
[quote]I bought this CD for Roseanne Cash's wonderful song Seven Year Ache and I was very pleased to find that one of my favorite country singers Patsy Cline is also featured on this CD with her fantastic song Walkin' After Midnight, other great songs are Loretta Lynn's Don't Come Home A'Drinkin' (With Lovin" On Your Mind), and Pam Tillis' Cleopatra, Queen Of Denial, plus many other good songs. If you love country music than I highly recommend this excellent CD, and even if you aren't into country music you still might like this CD, it's awesome!
[/quote]
